}}'''Djibouti''' is a [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in June 2019. Its default cities are only the capital, Djibouti.

On June 9, 2019 on [[IOS version|iOS]]; new countries were added. Along with Djibouti; there was also [[Afghanistan]], [[Belgium]], [[Dominican Republic]], [[Iraq]], [[Poland]], [[Puerto Rico]], [[Switzerland]], [[Taiwan]], [[Thailand]], [[United Arab Emirates]], and [[Uruguay]]. It was added to Android September 21, 2019.

== Trivia ==
* When the player has a conversation with another NPC, one of the topics they can discuss about is the size of Djibouti. This is probably a reference to the small size of the country.

